288
00:15:53,852 --> 00:15:56,295
that this particular user likes lions,

289
00:15:56,836 --> 00:16:00,660
and now it tries to offer them accessories for lions.

290
00:16:01,882 --> 00:16:04,645
In this way, we get from grapeshot shooting

291
00:16:05,226 --> 00:16:08,129
to very aimed sniper precision offers.

292
00:16:10,162 --> 00:16:12,383
The second principle is bargaining.

293
00:16:12,463 --> 00:16:15,264
It is basically, if you're turning down the offer,

294
00:16:15,684 --> 00:16:17,945
