295
00:16:18,406 --> 00:16:21,427
It will have lower price or higher value.

296
00:16:22,187 --> 00:16:25,229
But if we used only these two principles,

297
00:16:25,709 --> 00:16:29,051
the best behavior to address this system

298
00:16:29,091 --> 00:16:30,852
would be to turn down every offer,

299
00:16:30,892 --> 00:16:31,952
to decline every offer,

300
00:16:32,152 --> 00:16:34,413
till you get the maximum value for the lowest price.

301
00:16:36,094 --> 00:16:37,935
That is why we've added the third principle,

302
00:16:37,995 --> 00:16:40,336
which is randomness to avoid predictability.

